<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Monu Kumar | UPSC Aspirant</title>

<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

<style>

body{
margin:0;
font-family:Arial;
background:#f5f5f5;
}

header{
background:#1e3c72;
color:white;
padding:40px;
text-align:center;
}

.profile{
text-align:center;
margin-top:-60px;
}

.profile img{
width:180px;
border-radius:50%;
border:6px solid white;
}

.container{
max-width:900px;
margin:auto;
padding:20px;
}

.card{
background:white;
padding:20px;
margin:20px 0;
border-radius:10px;
box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

h2{
color:#1e3c72;
}

.btn{
display:inline-block;
padding:10px 20px;
background:#1e3c72;
color:white;
border-radius:5px;
text-decoration:none;
}

footer{
background:#1e3c72;
color:white;
text-align:center;
padding:10px;
margin-top:30px;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
<h1>Monu Kumar</h1>
<p>UPSC Aspirant | Student</p>
</header>

<div class="profile">
<img src="monu.jpg">
</div>

<div class="container">

<div class="card">
<h2>About Me</h2>
<p>
My name is <b>Monu Kumar</b>. I am from <b>Bundi, Rajasthan</b>.
I have completed my <b>BSTC</b> and <b>Bachelor of Arts (B.A)</b>.
Currently I am preparing for the <b>UPSC Civil Services Examination</b>
with the goal of serving the country as a civil servant.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>Education</h2>
<p>BSTC – Completed</p>
<p>Bachelor of Arts (B.A) – Completed</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>Career Goal</h2>
<p>
My dream is to clear the UPSC examination and serve India
through Civil Services.
</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>Social Media</h2>
<a class="btn" href="https://www.instagram.com/monumeenau" target="_blank">
Visit Instagram
</a>
</div>

</div>

<footer>
© 2026 Monu Kumar | Bundi Rajasthan
</footer>

</body>
</html>
